{"tid":2026332,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美軍AC-130J砲艇機 配備雷射武器","createTime":"2020-05-21T01:26:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-21T03:17:48.000Z","uid":54373,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"befe7cc0aba79cc620f60e0179e55aa90fc0e0a6","tid":2026332,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T01:26:41.000Z","msg":"空軍特種作戰司令部(AFSOC)表示，將在2022年之前，在AC-130J砲艇機上安裝高能雷射武器。<br />\n<br />\n國際防衛雜誌(National Defense)報導，美國空軍司令部固定翼計劃執行長梅利莎&middot;強生上校(Melissa Johnson)說， AFSOC與海軍水面作戰中心合作研發雷射武器，已經有5年之久，進行了一系列研究和地面測試。<br />\n<br />\n她說：「我非常期待最後成果，雷射武器將會是未來的裝備」<br />\n<br />\n報導稱，目前的測試都是地面上行，但是到2022年，就會將雷射武器安裝在飛機上測試。她指出，雷射武器的能量功率是60千瓦。<br />\n<br />\n最近，雷射武器正式納入了AC-130J計劃，也就是，AC-130J將成為雷射武器的載台。<br />\n<br />\nAC-130J是新一代的美國空軍砲艇機，稱為「幽靈騎士」(Ghostride)，它具有比前一代C-130H更大的機身，也就有更好的裝載量、航程和滯空時間，目前已達到初始作戰狀態。<br />\n<br />\n軍事網(<a href=\"http://Military.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FMilitary.com&d=JWMo9xAWlgSpyjxIujWPsR5ZC4%2B%2BlHDPeg0yH0hWprM%3D&h=d66966d5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Military.com</a>)報導，AC-130的飛行指揮官湯姆&middot;帕倫斯克（Tom Palenske）相當期待雷射武器的到來，他已經在思考，未來特種作戰上，雷射武器的使用場合。<br />\n<br />\n帕倫斯克說，雷射是重要王牌武器，它的瞬間指向性，能攔截其他的武器系統，並且能進行更精準的突擊作戰。<br />\n<br />\n他說：「假如有了雷射武器，要再執行一次擒拿諾瑞加(Manuel Noriega)的任務，那麼行動會比當年還要簡單，只要先用雷射將他的汽車引擎上燒個洞，使其癱瘓，再派海豹隊去抓捕就行。」<br />\n<br />\n帕倫斯克說的是是1989年，美國入侵巴拿馬，抓補諾瑞加的「正當行動」(Operation Just Cause)。<br />\n<br />\n高能雷射已超過肉眼可見，所以遭到攻擊的車輛只會感覺到一陣熱，然後車子就壞了，沒有噪音，沒有大驚小怪，沒人知道它發生了。<br />\n<br />\n其實，研究進度已經落後了，AFSOC曾希望今年就雷射武器整合到飛機上。但是資金不足，使得工作只能延遲。"},{"pid":"3bde7d201730dc3bb12c57a37cb5d28c71d13426","tid":2026332,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T01:27:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.nationaldefensemagazine.org/articles/2020/5/13/afsoc-on-track-to-demonstrate-airborne-laser-by-2022\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nationaldefensemagazine.org%2Farticles%2F2020%2F5%2F13%2Fafsoc-on-track-to-demonstrate-airborne-laser-by-2022&d=JWMo9xAWlgSpyjxIujWPsR5ZC4%2B%2BlHDPeg0yH0hWprM%3D&h=2128d6ab\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.nationaldefensemagazine.org/articles/2020/5/13/afsoc-on-track-to-demonstrate-airborne-laser-by-2022</a>"},{"pid":"fdffab2f740081b62185c2725002886e34d22ae7","tid":2026332,"uid":85461,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T01:31:17.000Z","msg":"裝到落B2既話就真係冇人知<br />\n做咩都得"},{"pid":"4b763dc86847a972b38e6e2ed174c25a71ac6e7e","tid":2026332,"uid":162075,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T01:33:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xVKOc0E.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxVKOc0E.png&h=29a7b4e6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c3571f43ce6fa1c2a1da0deaa7b5c9a596a5faa0","tid":2026332,"uid":156913,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T01:37:30.000Z","msg":"唔係話耗電勁咩？<br />\n解決咗？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ef9141abb637dd8c11fe4c0fdb3ac7de88e6c49","tid":2026332,"uid":54373,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"c3571f43ce6fa1c2a1da0deaa7b5c9a596a5faa0","tid":2026332,"uid":156913,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T01:37:30.000Z","msg":"唔係話耗電勁咩？<br />\n解決咗？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T01:39:50.000Z","msg":"美軍講得既野，已經發明咗20-30年"},{"pid":"47737bce5262a0ab27171aeb279314ceabe4aa74","tid":2026332,"uid":124400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T01:49:49.000Z","msg":"美國爸爸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3183238d9083262e1757082b667564ab8f0a51e","tid":2026332,"uid":151074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T01:53:02.000Z","msg":"呀群入黎帶路啦"},{"pid":"57e20bf6b2478ca9ee784e515be77a798a182fe8","tid":2026332,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c3571f43ce6fa1c2a1da0deaa7b5c9a596a5faa0","tid":2